Bootstrap classes

    .container
    .container-fluid
    .row


  .col-sm-pull-2
  .col-sm-push-8
     These type classes are used to shift the column left and right defends on the screen size.


  .visible-md  class is used to adjust the element to be visible im medium size
  .hidden-md hide an element in the medium size


Bootstrap navbar classes
    .navbar-nav
    .navbar-header
    .navbar-brand
    .navbar-left
    .navbar-right
    .navbar-form
    .navbar-toggle

    navbar-inverse class make the navbar dark

    navbar-fixed-top class fix the navbar on top.it will help to access the menu where you are in the page

    in order to get the navbar to shrink when we scroll down, we need to include a third party library from github.

    to makean image responsive use 'img-responsive' class im the image tag

